              "free_text": [
                " For the Sm(n,gamma) samples commercial",
                "samarium was purified by two Na analgem separations.",
                "No attempt was to remove Eu, but the various neutron",
                "radiations of Eu2O3 revealed the absence of any",
                "short-lived Eu isotopes with half-lives less than the",
                "reported 9.2 h. Counting through various absorbers",
                "was begun immediately after the end of the irradiation."
              ]
